data.description: Charming 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Home with 1-Car Garage and Expansive Backyard!    Welcome to this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled in a prime location, within walking distance to both elementary and high schools. Convenience is key with a short stroll to H-E-B, Walmart, and Starbucks, catering to your daily needs. The property boasts a spacious 1-car garage and a large backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and relaxation.    Recent upgrades include a brand new roof, ensuring worry-free living for years to come. While the home offers a solid foundation, it's ready for your personal touch - a canvas awaiting your creative updates and paint choices.     Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to transform this house into your dream home. Enjoy the ease of access to schools, shopping, and amenities, coupled with the potential to create a space that truly reflects your style and comfort.
